msgctxt "892"
msgid "Thick Businessman"
msgstr "Hombre de negocios gordo"

msgctxt "896"
msgid "Skinny Businessman"
msgstr "Hombre de negocios delgado"

msgctxt "900"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "904"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "84_Thick Businessman"
msgid "Something fishy's going on in this town, I just know it.\\r\n"\n"Things aren't usually this... earsplitting."
msgstr "Algo está sucediendo en esta ciudad, lo sé.\\r\n"\n"Las cosas no suelen ser tan estridentes."

msgctxt "96_Skinny Businessman"
msgid "I dunno, man. It's always pretty dang loud around here."
msgstr "No lo sé. Esto siempre suele ser bastante ruidoso."

msgctxt "108_Thick Businessman"
msgid "Loud is one thing, but I heard ambulances earlier! That's\\r\n"\n"not normal!"
msgstr "Ruidoso es una cosa, ¡pero he oído ambulancias antes! ¡Eso\\r\n"\n"no es normal!"

msgctxt "120_Skinny Businessman"
msgid "Uh, yes it is. I think you're just overthinking it."
msgstr "Eh, sí, lo es. Creo que lo estás sobrepensando."

